# Coding Guidelines

- My project's programming language is python 3.11
- Use early returns when possible
- Always add documentation when creating new functions and classes

<!-- ## Project Structure -->

## Database & ORM

- Use mariadb for database operations

## Testing

- Always use uv run to execute .py files.
- Use pytest for testing

## Security

- Use FastAPI's built-in security features
- Implement proper authentication using JWT
- Use HTTPS for all production endpoints

## Performance

- Use async/await patterns where appropriate
- Implement proper caching strategies

## Documentation

- Use proper docstrings for all functions and classes
- Maintain README.md with setup instructions

## Development Practices

- Use git for version control
- Write meaningful commit messages
